quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  5,115,"Allâh said: "
  5,116,"And (remember) when Allâh will say (on the Day of Resurrection): "
  5,117,""
  6,76,"When the night covered him over with darkness he saw a star. He said: "
  6,77,"When he saw the moon rising up, he said: "
  6,78,"When he saw the sun rising up, he said: "